    dc:creator "Hernández-Corral, Jesús" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "The spider family Dysderidae in the Balearic Islands" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1003036>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1003038>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1003044> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1003036>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Fig. 1. Dysdera arnedoi Lissner new species. Female, dorsalateral view. Figs 2 – 3. Dysdera crocata C. L. Koch (from St Elm). 2. Male, dorsal view; 3. Female, dorsal view; Figs 4 – 5. Dysdera lata ReUss, 1834; 4. Male, dorsal view; 5. Female, dorsal view. Fig. 6. Harpactea dufouri (Thorell, 1839); Male, dorsal view. Fig. 7. Parachtes riberai Bosmans new species; Male, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1003036/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1003038>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 16. Figs 8 – 14. Dysdera arnedoi Lissner new species; 8. Prosoma, dorsal view; 9. Left chelicera, ventral view; 10. FemUr IV, dorsal view; 11. MetatarsUs and tarsUs I, lateral view; 12. Tarsal claw, pectination only drawn for one claw; 13. VUlva, dorsal view; 14. VUlva, ventral view. Figs 15 – 16. Harpactea dufouri (Thorell, 1873). 15. Male palp, retrolateral view (from Estellencs); 16. VUlva, dorsal view (from Palma, Castilla de San Carlos). Scale bars: 8: 2 mm, 9: 0.5 mm, 10, 11: 1 mm, 12: 0.1 mm, 13 – 16: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1003038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1003044>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27 – 30. Figs 27 – 28. Dysdera balearica Thorell, 1873; 27. VUlva, ventral view; 28. Idem, dorsal view. Fig. 29. Dysdera lata ReUss, 1834. VUlva, dorsal view. Figs 30 – 32. Dysdera arnedoi new species. 30. VUlva, dorsal view with transversal bar still in place; 31. Idem, ventral view; 32. Idem, dorsal view. Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1003044/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

